name: StrokeOrderTypes
shortdesc: Options for displaying row and column strokes at corners.

property.name: ROW_ON_TOP
property.shortdesc: Places row strokes in front of column strokes.

property.name: COLUMN_ON_TOP
property.shortdesc: Places column strokes in front of row strokes.

property.name: BEST_JOINS
property.shortdesc: Places row strokes in front of column strokes when row and column strokes are different colors; joins striped strokes and connects crossing points.

property.name: INDESIGN_2_COMPATIBILITY
property.shortdesc: Places row strokes in front when row and column strokes are different colors; joins striped strokes only at points where strokes cross in a T-shape.
